ation			</li>		<li><A HREF="dnd/index.html">Dungeons &amp; Dragons</A>		- The math in D&amp;D, maps and calenders for Greyhawk, notes on character advancement, and campaign journals.			</li>		<li><A HREF="do-transcript.html">Do: Pilgrims of the Flying Temple Journal</A>		- Transcript of a Do game played August 3, 2011 at Gen Con Indy.			</li>		<li><A HREF="dungeon-world/index.html">Dungeon World</A>		- The game inspired by early Dungeons &amp; Dragons and modern narrative focused design.			</li>		<li><A HREF="leverage/index.html">Leverage</A>		- Resources for Margaret Weis Production's Leverage: The Roleplaying Game, based on the television show Leverage.			</li>		<li><A HREF="my-life-with-master/index.html">My Life With Master</A>		- Resources for the RPG My Life With Master.			</li>		<li><A HREF="paranoia/index.html">Paranoia</A>		- Resources for the Paranoia role-playing game.			</li>		<li><A HREF="shadowrun/index.html">Shadowrun</A>		- Shadowrun survival tips for players and several campaign journals.			</li>		<li><A HREF="spirit-of-the-century/index.html">Spirit of the Century</A>		- Resources for Spirit of the Century			</li>		<li><A HREF="swords-and-wizardry/index.html">Swords &amp; Wizardry</A>		- Mythmere Game's clone of original Dungeons &amp; Dragons			</li>	</ul><div class="footerinfo"><a href="../email.html">Contact webmaster</a></div></div></div></body></html>
